Subject: [PATCH 092/254] arm: socfpga: Enable MTD flash device for socfpga

Upstream: git://git.rocketboards.org/linux-socfpga.git

-Add MTD flash device to socfpga_defconfig

Signed-off-by: Dinh Nguyen <dinguyen@altera.com>
(cherry picked from commit 8f9815ae5af9e004e891a08f2e9c5b5eb263063f)
Signed-off-by: Zumeng Chen <zumeng.chen@windriver.com>
---
 arch/arm/configs/socfpga_defconfig |    4 ++++
 1 files changed, 4 insertions(+), 0 deletions(-)

diff --git a/arch/arm/configs/socfpga_defconfig b/arch/arm/configs/socfpga_defconfig
index e36c05a..39d2f66 100644
--- a/arch/arm/configs/socfpga_defconfig
+++ b/arch/arm/configs/socfpga_defconfig
@@ -42,6 +42,10 @@ CONFIG_IP_PNP_BOOTP=y
 CONFIG_IP_PNP_RARP=y
 CONFIG_UEVENT_HELPER_PATH="/sbin/hotplug"
